summary: Oh earlier my private lessons teacher was showing me this shakespeare encyclopedia she has with info about all the plays and...
body: Oh earlier my private lessons teacher was showing me this shakespeare encyclopedia she has with info about all the plays and pictures from different adaptations and she flipped through the pages really quickly but for a split second… I saw him. She let me look at it and I was like oh hmm gonna look at, idk, the hamlet section for no apparent reason, and BAM, full page photo of David Tennant and I was like “ah yes I thought I saw him” and my teacher was like “oh of course if you see David Tennant in his hamlet crown you have to stop and look” so long story short, Christine is a DT Stan and I’ve never felt more connected to her
